A consortium including RMB Ventures and RMB Corvest recently bought 100% of Kevro, Africa’s largest supplier of corporate and promotional apparel and other branded goods. Sasha Planting talks to Mbongeni Madonsela and Khuthadzo Masindi from RMB Ventures about the deal and the company’s opportunities for growth. For other RMB transactions watch: The ideal private equity purchase RMB facilitates Distell Group’s complex shareholding restructure Brought to you by RMB.  